Compilation:

Windows:
//g++ or gcc installed using mingw:
go to root directory and paste this in the terminal:
g++ -fdiagnostics-color=always -g -I./game/dependencies/nlohmann -o ./game/game.exe ./game/game.cpp ./game/utilitieS.cpp

Playing the game:
//once compiled, go to the game/ folder and execute this in powershell terminal:
.\game
NOTE: it is important to go to game\ folder for the savefiles to load!!!
